    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 straight-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is excellent, featuring a recently serviced VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe to handle the torque loads from the variable M differential lock. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers. While the exterior shows honest signs of use, the powertrain exhibits optimal compression and a crisp throttle response. A mechanically transparent example primed for the B-roads.",
