    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily usability and spirited performance. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the leather seating is supple and free of cracks, the carpets are pristine, and every switch and dial operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service folder. It recently underwent a full multi-point inspection, including a fresh oil service and a brake fluid flush. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. With four matching tires showing deep tread and a clean, smoke-free interior, this car is ready for immediate enjoyment without the need for upcoming maintenance.",
