      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been a fantastic ride and is still in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and ready for all your adventures! It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, making it a great find for anyone wanting a dependable vehicle. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take it for a spin!",
