    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 with its signature individual throttle bodies. This unit boasts a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing versatile suspension geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes updated rod bearings and throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction system operate at peak efficiency. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain and subframe integrity are uncompromising. A pure driver\u2019s machine for those who prioritize longitudinal and lateral G-loading precision.",
